        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1871780280" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer9089095479024693992">Enjoyable historical mystery set in England during World War II. This has all the usual trappings; aristocratic young ladies, brave RAF pilots, spies, two plucky children, a vicar, a bit of romance and a somewhat predictable ending. A solid, easy on the brain read.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


